title: Letter from the President on the Cuban Liberty and Democratic Solidarity (LIBERTAD) Act of 1996 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
January 15, 2010

 



Letter from the President on the Cuban Liberty and Democratic Solidarity (LIBERTAD) Act of 1996




Attached is a letter from the President to the Chairman and Ranking Member of the House Committee on Foreign Affairs, Chairmen and Ranking Members of The House and Senate Committees on Appropriations, and The Chairman and Ranking Member of the Senate Committee on Foreign Relations.
